		<title>뉴질랜드行 회견 앞두고 주목받는 GBP/NZD 환율</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/ko/analysis/market-news/gbpnzd-in-focus-rbnz-conference</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 18:12:46 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[마켓 뉴스 및 자료]]></category>
